===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

# A [[long]], [[thin]], sharp [[implement]] usually for [[pierce|piercing]] as in [[sew]]ing, [[embroidery]], [[acupuncture]], [[tattoo]]ing, [[body]] [[piercing]], [[medical]] [[injection]]s, [[suture]]s, etc; or a blunt but otherwise similar implement used for forming [[loop]]s or [[knot]]s in crafts such as [[darning]], [[knit]]ting, [[tatting]], etc.
