#: ''a compass '''needle'''''
#: {{ux|en|The '''needle''' on the fuel gauge pointed to empty.}}
# A [[sensor]] for playing [[phonograph]] [[record]]s, a phonograph [[stylus]].
#: {{ux|en|Ziggy bought some diamond '''needles''' for his hi-fi phonograph.}}
# A needle-like leaf found on some [[conifers]].
#* {{quote-book|en|1994|[[w:Stephen Fry|Stephen Fry]]|[[w:The Hippopotamus|The Hippopotamus]]|chapter=2|passage=At the very moment he cried out, David realised that what he had run into was only the Christmas tree. Disgusted with himself at such cowardice, he spat a '''needle''' from his mouth.}}
# A strong beam resting on props, used as a [[temporary]] [[support]] during building repairs.
