# {{lb|en|programming}} A [[text]] [[string]] that is [[search]]ed for within another string. (see: [[needle in a haystack]])
#* {{quote-book|en|2010|Peter MacIntyre|PHP: The Good Parts|page=39|passage=Both of these functions will look through the haystack for the specified '''needle''' and, if they find it, will return the portion of the string from the beginning of the needle to the end of the haystack.}}
